title: Catherine Feeny - 2006 - Hurricane Glass
description:
Catherine Feeny (born 1976) is a critically-acclaimed singer/songwriter based in Portland, Oregon.

With producer Sebastian Rogers, she produced her second album: &#039;Hurricane Glass&#039;, which was released in the UK in June 2006. It includes the single &#039;Mr Blue&#039; which features in the 2006 film Running With Scissors, starring Annette Bening and Gwyneth Paltrow and based on the Augusten Burroughs book of the same name.
